Fana vayandikiligwe muna yamaandiko, "Niyamulonda Yakobo, mbali niyamwihilwa Esau."
Maabaho chilihi chihalongigwe? Mulungu ni yehile? Nehado!
Kwaviya Mulungu kamulongela Musa, "Nizamuwonela ubazi munhu yoyose yondonele ubazi, na niye nizawonela ubazi munhu yoyose yondonele ubazi."
