Fana viyandikile Mulungu muna chitabu cha Hoseya, "Nizamchema 'Wanhu wangu' wala hawawele wanhu wa heni, na 'Mndele wangu' nizamchema 'Mndele wangu' ija siyo mndele wangu."
Kahi, "Na hanhu hoyawalongelelile, 'Hemwe si wanhu wa niye,' Baho wezatangigwa 'Wanhu wa Mulungu yeli na ugima.' "
Maabaho Isaya koguta kwa dizi kulu, "Hata waja wanhu wa Isilaeli wahata kuwa wengi fana matumbwi ya sambi da muulwanda, wawo waidumwe wezakomboligwa.
Kwaviya Mndewa kezatenda viyaviya kwa utaguso wake mwiisi yose, kwa himahima ng'hani!"
Viya fana Isaya vayalongile haulongozi wake, "Habali Mndewa Mndewa wa Malagilizo sigambe yatulechele ulelo, chilawilila fana sodoma, chilawilila fana Gomola."
Ivo tulonge choni, ivo wanhu weli siyo Wayahudi, wala hawawalondile wanhu watanganike, wagona wanhu watanganike kwa ichimu cha uhuwilo.
Mbali wanhu wa Isilaeli, wakala wozahila kuvifika wanhu watanganike kwa kuwinza Malagilizo, hawadahile bule.
